rows.label: qst500106_msg0001
rows.name: Hello-lo!

rows.label: qst500106_msg0002
rows.name:
Simama come here to search for
tasty-tasty juice ingredients.

rows.label: qst500106_msg0003
rows.name: But only find lots of Cloud Sea.

rows.label: qst500106_msg0004
rows.name:
Other brotherpons and sisterpons
probably find ingredients and go back
home to Avaritia already...

rows.label: qst500106_msg0005
rows.name: What should Simama do?

rows.label: qst500106_msg0006
rows.name: What SHOULD Simama do?

rows.label: qst500106_msg0007
rows.name: Try salvaging!

rows.label: qst500106_msg0008
rows.name: Try gathering from a Divine Beast

rows.label: qst500106_msg0009
rows.name: Meh-meh-meh!

rows.label: qst500106_msg0010
rows.name:
Simama was so busy worrying,
did not even think of that!

rows.label: qst500106_msg0011
rows.name: Simama dive down right now!

rows.label: qst500106_msg0012
rows.name:
...Simama forgot to put on salvager suit,
but still found Angel Engine!

rows.label: qst500106_msg0013
rows.name:
Not look very tasty-tasty, but Simama
take this back home anyway!

rows.label: qst500106_msg0014
rows.name:
Other brotherpons and sisterpons of
Simama also searching for ingredients,
so probably this enough for now.

rows.label: qst500106_msg0015
rows.name:
Friends say hello-lo if seeing
any of them!

rows.label: qst500106_msg0016
rows.name: Bye-bye now!

rows.label: qst500106_msg0017
rows.name: Meh-meh-meh!

rows.label: qst500106_msg0018
rows.name:
Oh! Simama not even notice that
Divine Beast right there behind Simama!

rows.label: qst500106_msg0019
rows.name:
Divine Beast even covered in greenery!
Probably full of tasty-tasty veggies!

rows.label: qst500106_msg0020
rows.name:
Simama will find ingredients and
take ship straight back home!

rows.label: qst500106_msg0021
rows.name:
Drop by Twelve Brothersisterpon
drinks place at Avaritia if friends
want, and say hello-lo to Simama again!
